Megascops
=========

 Dependencies
 ------------

 * django
   pip install django
 * gearman
   sudo apt-get install gearman
 * django-gearman
   pip install -e git://github.com/fwenzel/django-gearman.git#egg=django-gearman
 * django-registration
   pip install django-registration
 * quvi
   sudo apt-get build-dep libquvi
   sudo apt-get install libtool gengetopt
   git clone git://repo.or.cz/quvi.git
   cd quvi
   ./autogen.sh
   ./configure [--enable-nsfw]
   make
   sudo make install
